<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870105-0058 </DOCNO><HL> Arkla Purchases Arkoma,Owner of Gas Reserves</HL><DD> 01/05/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> ALGTENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> SHREVEPORT, La.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Arkla Inc. said it purchased Arkoma Production Co., Fort Smith, Ark., for $14 million in cash and the assumption of $35 million in liabilities.    Arkla, a natural gas producer and distributor, said that Arkoma owns more than 50 billion cubic feet of proven natural gas reserves, among other assets. </TEXT></DOC>